The CyberTipline Report indicated that the Synchronoss Technologies account associated with 443-754-5748 was utilized to upload the reported child pornography files. 

I conducted a query of the phone number through an open-source database and determined that it is registered to Verizon Wireless and geo-locates to Salisbury, Wicomico County, Maryland.

I transmitted an investigative subpoena request to the Wicomico County Office of the State's Attorney for Verizon and submitted a written preservation request for the reported account to Synchronoss Technologies, Inc.

Case open, investigation continuing.
